title: Looking for duo partner
body:
Looknig for someone to and duo with me, im silver 3 but have an s5 account that im trying to climb with.
Message me on here or add me "The Ranga Chap" and ill look forward to palying with you :)
cheers.

replies.body: Hey man! I main support and have been playing lol for under half a year now. I am Bronze 3 with 7 wins out of 22 games and 99 LP. May not be as high level as you, but I main support and it's always my first pick in ranked, so I hope I can help you climb!  :)
